name: Army Fighter- Strike War Jet
description:
Army Fighter- Strike War Jet is being carried out at enemy base. Feel the power of modern jet fighters and combat air strike war planes in this amazing war simulator 3D
Features:

• Action Combat Flight Simulator Game.
• Modern Jet Fighter Models.
• Advance Controls & Manoeuvrability.
• Multiple war and air strike missions.
• Action packed combat flight game.
• Realistic dogfight simulation.
